name: SinisterRaven
description:
This model renowned for creating artistic style, future realistic fantasy portraits, and captivating landscapes.

The recommended VAE architecture, sd-vae-ft-mse-original, and the Sampler DPM++2M Karras (25 to 35+ steps) method to generate diverse and high-quality outputs.

I also recommend using the hypernetwork hypernetwork-quality-tags for the best quality.

Unleash your creativity and bring your visions to life with SinisterRaven's immersive and imaginative capabilities.
